premise_source_doc_sentence: The Adventures of Tintin , known as The Adventures of Tintin : The Secret of the Unicorn outside North America , is a 2011 3D motion capture computer-animated mystery action-adventure film based on The Adventures of Tintin , the comics series by Belgian cartoonist Hergé .
